Advantages and Disadvantages of Conversion of Credits to Swiss Francs
In the banking market there have already appeared two offers of conversion in lei of loans in Swiss francs, the main advantages being the exclusion of currency risk and the reduction of rates.
Disadvantages can come in a few years, when the variable interest rate can lead to an increase in rates.
Transylvania Bank has just completed the process of converting loans into francs granted by Volksbank, and Bancpost has announced the conversion offer for its own customers.
